content: Sen Hassan, you are a disgrace not only to the state of NH, but to the whole US. I hope that this is your 1st and last time as being the senator from NH. You are a prefect example of a snowflake that can’t think for herself. If your leader from New York had to stop quick, they would need a chain fall to pull you out of his ass. Do the right thing and lets get this country heading forward. Vote to put judge Gorsuch on the Supreme court.
